{% doc %}
  @prompt
    **AI Prompt:**
    
    Create a Shopify product carousel section with off-white background. Center-aligned heading "OUR GOODS" in bold, extra-heavy black sans-serif (80-90px). Below it, subtitle in regular sans-serif (28-32px) "You'll be cooking like Carmy in no time." 
    
    Horizontal scrollable product cards with thick black borders (8-10px), rounded corners (20px), light gray background. Each card contains product image with rounded corners. Bright neon green starburst badge (top-right) with "HOME MADE!" in bold black text, jagged edges.
    
    Product name below image in bold uppercase black text (24px). Price "$12.00" centered beneath (22px). Product description in regular black text (18px), 2-3 lines, centered.
    
    Bottom-right: two circular navigation arrows (60px diameter), neon green background, black arrows, black borders. Cards have subtle shadows. Spacing: 60px top/bottom padding, 40px between elements, 20px card gaps. Modern, bold, playful aesthetic with high contrast.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
